brainrot-trigger-desc-police = You seem to have confused the post-soviet era with the far future of humanity.

brainrot-trigger-desc-generic =
    Signs of brainrot:
    - Internet memes and forced references.
    - 21st-century gaming and online slang, anglicisms for the sake of anglicisms.
    - Eyesore chat abbreviations, as if a middle schooler is typing.
    - Real-world current politics, including direct mentions of nationalities.
    Using such expressions, even if they are not currently listed in the triggers, may result in a ban.
